{"tid":446123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗男人對待妻子如AV女優，導致伊朗離婚率激增","createTime":"2017-10-24T04:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T12:05:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f018e5a5d0cc6aa544fd431d73a5e4c9c13274a9","tid":446123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://www.nownews.com/news/20170918/2609319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20170918%2F2609319&d=%2BhKbYXjbfNW7K7L3fU1SdqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d4b05dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nownews.com/news/20170918/2609319</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n丈夫待妻如AV女優、酷愛SM　導致伊朗離婚率激增<br />\n<br />\n伊朗最近10年來離婚例激增，連帶使出生率下滑，據稱這是因為許多伊朗男人和妻子共享魚水之歡時，時常模仿A片裡面的性虐待劇情瘋狂SM，導致枕邊人不滿，怒提離婚解脫噩夢。<br />\n<br />\n印度新德里電視台（NDTV）引述多名伊朗女性的說法，證實伊朗男人在床上時，確實對待妻子如AV女優。一名叫沙巴（Sabah）的女性表示，和丈夫上床時，曾被他用菸頭燒灼乳頭；還有一位叫莎拉（Sarah）的女性表示，丈夫迷戀成人影片的性虐待手法，曾被他銬上手銬，強迫進行類似影片的戲碼。<br />\n<br />\n有學者分析，這是因為伊朗的社會風氣較保守，使得男性獲得性知識的唯一途徑就是這些成人影片，使得他們在潛移默化之下，將妻子當成AV女優般的洩慾工具。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗總統發言人莫拉維迪（Shahindokht Molaverdi）日前表示，「性生活失調是伊朗離婚率節節攀升的主要原因」，當局將針對考慮離婚的夫妻，在全國各地設立家庭保健診所，以提供性生活諮詢服務。"},{"pid":"2f174ad7fda78d556fbf8f2a295ae3b81e567a98","tid":446123,"uid":90811,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"燒灼乳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916d85d92d4a64b1aba71f647d34d254f7e76d00","tid":446123,"uid":4550,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"班連登仔咪都係咁 總之女人就係雞<br />\n同印度班生番冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e551ba8d67466df5d9bfb9b7467e84c9584b7d4","tid":446123,"uid":1139,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af669fae5bae84392ab2852f825978e5c61e4f4e","tid":446123,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"真正嘅AV上腦<br />\n禁絕佢地睇av啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a024570678007ff8c1abf158c40a504e1d4641d","tid":446123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a5f3e58bbe93584f2e2de93d4fa4012cfc4b21","tid":446123,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"冇睇過一套會燒乳頭既AV"},{"pid":"a67f6ac218d72c1e8b7ebb96a3e209b336f37f4d","tid":446123,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班連登仔咪都係咁 總之女人就係雞<br />\n同印度班生番冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你大獲啦"},{"pid":"a79ad81da1a30e5dc960ded5503d6620b89d523e","tid":446123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcdccb19b5fcdf0e2f6ee612de6c374b4f0c3ca","tid":446123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}